Content: Do you need to do anything so you can tip and receive tipps?

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
@mato121 there is a list of commands in the pin.    The first time you dm the bot !deposit it will give you a KMD address specific to your name.    !tip balance/withdraw/info all work in dm.   
To tip in channels type !kmdtip (username) (amount)
